{"tid":2423980,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳肇始：10億疫苗保險只是備用 預計不會用盡","createTime":"2021-02-26T08:47:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T08:52:50.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"562fa32fa4755d1b2aa349d0e3555e80ae5f5d85","tid":2423980,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T08:47:12.000Z","msg":"政府向財委會申請10億撥款 用作疫苗補償基金<br />\n<br />\n食物及衛生局向立法會財務委員會申請10億元撥款，設立保障基金，向接種新冠疫苗後出現嚴重副作用或死亡的市民提供賠償。<br />\n<br />\n受影響人士要先得到註冊醫生證明，以及經專家委員會評估是否與接種疫苗相關，才可以提出索償，若果個案確立，死亡個案最多獲賠償250萬元，嚴重受傷個案則最多獲賠償300萬元。<br />\n<br />\n食衛局長陳肇始表示，保障基金只是有備無患，希望令市民安心，鼓勵接種率，預計不會用盡10億元，但若果有需要會再加碼；至於每宗個案如何釐定賠償額，當局稍後會制定並公開客觀標準，亦會設立機制，讓不滿意賠償額的人士提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2380748\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2380748&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd60cTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=bd98af8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2380748</a>"},{"pid":"10ec91d2b9a4d078150c822219c5abebdd87d781","tid":2423980,"uid":55914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T08:47:59.000Z","msg":"不會用盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係預左會用? 預左有人死?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49da309191cd7b6a088111377dd8e8e4f510bdae","tid":2423980,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10ec91d2b9a4d078150c822219c5abebdd87d781","tid":2423980,"uid":55914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T08:47:59.000Z","msg":"不會用盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係預左會用? 預左有人死?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T08:48:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ead63c1ede8f77a80379bf6f9e3bbd1d5d690147","tid":2423980,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply